To create a RESTful API in Flask that allows adding, updating, and retrieving user information from an in-memory dictionary, follow these steps. Ensure you have Flask installed in your environment (`pip install Flask`).

```python
from flask import Flask, jsonify, request

app = Flask(__name__)

# In-memory dictionary to store user data
users = {}

# Route to add or update user information
